OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDrought emergency declared 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin northern Italy          
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Italy has declared a state of emergency
OL,6, in five northern regions surrounding   
OL,7, the Po River amid the worse drought in 
OL,8, 70 years.                              
OL,10,FEmilia-Romagna, Friuli Venezia Giulia, 
OL,11,FLombardy, Piedmont and Veneto will be  
OL,12,Fgiven 36.5m euros (#31m; $38m) in      
OL,13,Femergency funds to tackle the water    
OL,14,Fshortage.                              
OL,16,FThe drought threatens more than 30% of 
OL,17,FItaly's agricultural produce, according
OL,18,Fto the agricultural union Coldiretti.  
OL,20,FSeveral municipalities have already    
OL,21,Fannounced water rationing.             
